    //- Main Content
    div(class="flex-1 py-12 px-6")
      div(class="max-w-3xl mx-auto")
        div(class="bg-discord-darkerBg rounded-xl p-8 shadow-discord")
          h1(class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2") Privacy Policy
          p(class="text-discord-textMuted text-sm mb-8") Last updated: January 2026
          
          div(class="space-y-8 text-discord-textNormal")
            section
              h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                span(class="w-6 h-6 bg-discord-green/20 text-discord-green rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold") 1
                | Information We Collect
              p(class="leading-relaxed mb-3") We collect the following information when you use our service:
              ul(class="list-none space-y-2 ml-8")
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Discord user ID, username, and avatar
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Email address (from Discord OAuth)
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Payment information (processed by Stripe)
            
            section
              h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                span(class="w-6 h-6 bg-discord-green/20 text-discord-green rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold") 2
                | How We Use Your Information
              p(class="leading-relaxed mb-3") We use your information to:
              ul(class="list-none space-y-2 ml-8")
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Process payments and verify purchases
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Assign premium roles to your Discord account
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Communicate with you about your account
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Improve our services
            
            section
              h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                span(class="w-6 h-6 bg-discord-green/20 text-discord-green rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold") 3
                | Data Storage and Security
              p(class="leading-relaxed") Your data is stored securely and we implement appropriate technical measures to protect your information. Payment data is handled entirely by Stripe and we do not store credit card information.
            
            section
              h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                span(class="w-6 h-6 bg-discord-green/20 text-discord-green rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold") 4
                | Third-Party Services
              p(class="leading-relaxed mb-3") We use the following third-party services:
              ul(class="list-none space-y-2 ml-8")
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Stripe — Payment processing
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Discord — Authentication and role management
            
            section
              h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                span(class="w-6 h-6 bg-discord-green/20 text-discord-green rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold") 5
                | Data Sharing
              p(class="leading-relaxed") We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to provide our services or as required by law.
            
            section
              h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                span(class="w-6 h-6 bg-discord-green/20 text-discord-green rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold") 6
                | Your Rights
              p(class="leading-relaxed mb-3") You have the right to:
              ul(class="list-none space-y-2 ml-8")
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Access your personal data
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Request deletion of your data
                li(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                  span(class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-discord-textMuted rounded-full")
                  | Opt out of marketing communications
            
            section
              h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                span(class="w-6 h-6 bg-discord-green/20 text-discord-green rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold") 7
                | Cookies
              p(class="leading-relaxed") We use session cookies to maintain your login state. These are essential for the service to function and are not used for tracking.
            
            section
              h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                span(class="w-6 h-6 bg-discord-green/20 text-discord-green rounded flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold") 8
                | Contact
              p(class="leading-relaxed") For privacy-related questions, please contact us through our Discord server.
              
        div(class="text-center mt-8")
          a(href="/" class="text-discord-textMuted text-sm hover:text-discord-textNormal transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2")
